=============================================<br />
<br />
         Dark Age of Camelot<br />
<br />
  Test Version 1.38B Release Notes<br />
<br />
           December 7, 2001 <br />
<br />
=============================================<br />
<br />
PATCH B (December 7, 2001)<br />
<br />
=======<br />
<br />
- Fixed a bug where Realm Rank 2 archers would sometimes do normal damage instead of critical damage with a critical shot.<br />
<br />
- Fixed a bug where a siege equipment could sometimes cause damage to members of the realm that built it.</font></p>
             
